  "detailed_description": "Treasure Journey is a 3D puzzle adventure where you guide a pirate across puzzling islands to uncover hidden treasures.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150150/extras/234280f6c2d4620ababb2fbac4e02df9.poster.avif?t=1721058220\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150150/extras/234280f6c2d4620ababb2fbac4e02df9.webm?t=1721058220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150150/extras/234280f6c2d4620ababb2fbac4e02df9.mp4?t=1721058220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Rotate and move the camera freely to find the best path.<br></li><li>Run, dig, and make clever use of gravity to overcome obstacles.<br></li><li>Collect keys to unlock treasure chests brimming with loot.<br></li><li>Upgrade your pirate's boots and shovel for a speedier, more powerful treasure hunt!<br></li><li>Explore diverse island environments, each with unique challenges.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150150/extras/523118612119f440e31016c5ffba1257.poster.avif?t=1721058220\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150150/extras/523118612119f440e31016c5ffba1257.webm?t=1721058220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150150/extras/523118612119f440e31016c5ffba1257.mp4?t=1721058220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Treasure Journey is a 3D puzzle adventure where you guide a pirate across puzzling islands to uncover hidden treasures.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150150/extras/234280f6c2d4620ababb2fbac4e02df9.poster.avif?t=1721058220\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150150/extras/234280f6c2d4620ababb2fbac4e02df9.webm?t=1721058220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150150/extras/234280f6c2d4620ababb2fbac4e02df9.mp4?t=1721058220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Rotate and move the camera freely to find the best path.<br></li><li>Run, dig, and make clever use of gravity to overcome obstacles.<br></li><li>Collect keys to unlock treasure chests brimming with loot.<br></li><li>Upgrade your pirate's boots and shovel for a speedier, more powerful treasure hunt!<br></li><li>Explore diverse island environments, each with unique challenges.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150150/extras/523118612119f440e31016c5ffba1257.poster.avif?t=1721058220\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150150/extras/523118612119f440e31016c5ffba1257.webm?t=1721058220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150150/extras/523118612119f440e31016c5ffba1257.mp4?t=1721058220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
